'''Nkuranga Lynder''' ni [[umugore]] w'umunyarwandakazi wari ukuriye ubutasi mu mahanga mu rwego rw'u [[Rwanda]] rishinzwe Umutekano ubu ni umukuru w'urwego rushinzwe abinjira n'abasohoka.<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/amakuru-58477515</ref>

== UBUZIMA BWITE ==
Assistant Commissioner of Police (ACP)<ref>https://www.police.gov.rw/home/</ref> '''Nkuranga Lynder''' [wavutse muri 1982], niwe [[Umugore|mugore]] wa mbere uyobora uru rwego rushinzwe imipaka, abinjira n'abasohoka, uburenganzira bwo gukorera mu [[Rwanda]],<ref>https://www.afrik.com/rwanda-qui-est-lynder-nkuranga-premiere-femme-a-diriger-les-services-secrets</ref> inyandiko z'inzira, ubwenegihugu n'ibindi.[https://www.migration.gov.rw/]<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/acp-linda-nkuranga-yagizwe-umuyobozi-muri-niss</ref><ref>https://en.igihe.com/news/article/acp-lynder-nkuranga-named-director-general-of-immigration-and-emigration</ref><ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/acp-lynder-nkuranga-yahawe-kuyobora-urwego-rw-abinjira-n-abasohoka</ref>

'''Nkuranga Lynder''', ufite [[imyaka]] 40, afite impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu bijyanye n'[[Amahoro (Akagari)|amahoro]] n'amakimbirane ndetse anitabira amasomo mu [[ishuri]] rya polisi rya [[Akarere ka Musanze|Musanze]].<ref>https://www.police.gov.rw/home/</ref> Amaze [[imyaka]] irenga icumi akora muri Polisi y'[[igihugu]] y'u [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/acp-linda-nkuranga-yagizwe-umuyobozi-muri-niss</ref><ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/acp-lynder-nkuranga-yahawe-kuyobora-urwego-rw-abinjira-n-abasohoka</ref> Umwuga we wabaye mwiza kandi byihuse kugeza ubu.<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/acp-linda-nkuranga-yagizwe-umuyobozi-muri-niss</ref><ref>https://en.igihe.com/news/article/acp-lynder-nkuranga-named-director-general-of-immigration-and-emigration</ref><ref>https://umuryango.rw/amakuru/mu-rwanda/politiki/article/byinshi-kuri-acp-lynder-nkuranga-wabaye-umugore-wa-mbere-uyoboye-urwego</ref><ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/amakuru-58477515</ref>

== Imiromo yakoze ==
'''Nkuranga Lynder''' yazamutse vuba mu mapeti mu gipolisi mu [[Imyaka|myaka]] igera ku 10,<ref>https://www.afrik.com/rwanda-qui-est-lynder-nkuranga-premiere-femme-a-diriger-les-services-secrets</ref> mu 2018 we n'abandi [[Umugore|bagore]] babiri Rose Muhisoni na Teddy Ruyenzi bahawe ipeti rya ACP (Assistant Commissioner of Police)<ref>https://www.police.gov.rw/home/</ref>. '''Lynder Nkuranga''' yari amaze [[umwaka]] [[Rimwe|umwe]] akuriye ishami ry'ubutasi mu mahanga mu rwego rw'u [[Rwanda]] rushinzwe umutekano National Intelligence and Security Services (NISS)<ref>https://sobanukirwa.rw/body/niss</ref> <ref>https://umuryango.rw/amakuru/mu-rwanda/politiki/article/byinshi-kuri-acp-lynder-nkuranga-wabaye-umugore-wa-mbere-uyoboye-urwego</ref>. Icyo gihe nibo [[Umugore|bagore]] ba mbere bari bageze hejuru cyane mu mapeti y'igipolisi mu [[Rwanda]],<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/acp-lynder-nkuranga-yahawe-kuyobora-urwego-rw-abinjira-n-abasohoka</ref> nyuma ya '''Mary Gahonzire''' wageze ku rwego rwa komiseri. '''Nkuranga''' yakoze imirimo itandukanye muri polisi irimo :<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/acp-linda-nkuranga-yagizwe-umuyobozi-muri-niss</ref><ref>https://en.igihe.com/news/article/acp-lynder-nkuranga-named-director-general-of-immigration-and-emigration</ref><ref>https://www.afrik.com/rwanda-qui-est-lynder-nkuranga-premiere-femme-a-diriger-les-services-secrets</ref><ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/amakuru-58477515</ref>

* kuba umukuru w'ibiro bya komiseri mukuru wa polisi y'u [[Rwanda]].
* Yanabaye umuvugizi wungirije wa polisi.<ref>https://umuryango.rw/amakuru/mu-rwanda/politiki/article/byinshi-kuri-acp-lynder-nkuranga-wabaye-umugore-wa-mbere-uyoboye-urwego</ref>
* Yabaye kandi umukuru w'urwego rwa [[Kigali]] International Conference Declaration  (KICD) ruhuriwemo n'abagore mu nzego z'umutekano z'ibihugu 42 bya Africa, rugamije kurwanya ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsinda n'ihohoterwa rikorerwa abana.<ref>https://www.icglr-rtf.org/6th-kigali-international-conference-declaration-kicd-annual-general-meeting-on-the-role-of-security-organs-to-end-violence-against-women-and-girls/</ref> <ref>https://police.gov.rw/fileadmin/templates/images/News-2016/RNP_-_KICD_Supplement.pdf</ref><ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/amakuru-58477515</ref>
* Umwaka ushize, mbere yo kugirwa ukuriye ubutasi mu mahanga yari komiseri ushinzwe ubutwererane na protocol muri polisi.<ref>https://www.police.gov.rw/home/</ref><ref>https://www.afrik.com/rwanda-qui-est-lynder-nkuranga-premiere-femme-a-diriger-les-services-secrets</ref><ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/acp-lynder-nkuranga-yahawe-kuyobora-urwego-rw-abinjira-n-abasohoka</ref>
* '''Nkuranga Lynder''' umwe mu bagore bacye bari mu rwego rwo hejuru mu mapeti ya polisi y'u Rwanda usigaye ari umukuru w'urwego rushinzwe abinjira n'abasohoka.<ref>https://www.migration.gov.rw/</ref><ref>https://umuryango.rw/amakuru/mu-rwanda/politiki/article/byinshi-kuri-acp-lynder-nkuranga-wabaye-umugore-wa-mbere-uyoboye-urwego</ref><ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/amakuru-58477515</ref>

